title: G-IP 2: Display Post Rug GLX Snapshot List
body:
{Summary/ Plan A}
Should we display the GLX post rug Snapshot list

{Priority and Curb Appeal}
List milestones in priority
Milestone 1:
Vote 


Abstract, Why, How, When
A Snapshot was taken a few hours post rug
Some are worried they might not be in it due to selling the rug 
Informal Vote says show the list 
This is a formal vote to show the list


Team Necessary for Milestone: 
The community

Milestone 2:
IF vote to show, show the list 
Time between M1-M2
immediate 
Caveats if no more allowance after M2
Milestone 3:
Informal vote to add community members that sold the rug 
Time between M2-M3
immediate
Milestone 4: 
Formal Vote to add community members that sold the rug
Time between M2-M3
immediate
Milestone 5: 
IF vote to readd field requests to readd those that sold the rug

Commercialization & Future Proofing Strategy
will bring a better sense of the community



{Manifestations}
bigger community drive

{Funding}
no funding needed

{Your commitment to the Dao}
lifer


I ___futjr__ hereby swear to this proposal as being thoughtout, derived from a desire to succeed, and for my fellow players.
